<Layout title="Studio Ghibli | スタジオジブリ" description="About Studio Ghibli">
    <div class="min-h-[70vh] flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-center px-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2">Studio Ghibli</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-4">A world-renowned Japanese animation studio celebrated for its animated films.</p>
        <div class="max-w-xl text-gray-500">
            <p>Founded in 1985 by filmmakers Hayao Miyazaki, Isao Takahata, and producer Toshio Suzuki, the studio has produced over 20 feature films. Notable titles include "My Neighbor Totoro," "Spirited Away," and "Princess Mononoke."</p>
            <p class="mt-2">Known for its detailed animations, vivid characters, and emotional narratives, Studio Ghibli has captivated audiences of all ages around the globe.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
